u1ea9y \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111i ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc. Sau \u0111\u00f3 1 ph\u00fat, Lacazette \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh nh\u01b0ng Oblak k\u1ecbp ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1.</span></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ket qua Arsenal vs Atletico Madrid ban ket Europa League 2018 hinh anh\" title=\"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Arsenal vs Atletico Madrid b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/26/truc-tiep-arsenal-vs-atletico-madrid-02h05-ngay-274-europa-league-201718.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ebfn ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 9, Welbeck d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb g\u1ea7n v\u1ea1ch 16m50 nh\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u00f3  \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Oblak. B\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 10 khi Vrsaljko nh\u1eadn  th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng th\u1ee9 hai, \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n t\u1eeb s\u1ea5t s\u1edbm. Kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n c\u00e0ng  th\u00eam ch\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid khi HLV Diego Simeone b\u1ecb tru\u1ea5t quy\u1ec1n ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o  ba ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi, Arsenal li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng pha h\u00e3m th\u00e0nh nguy hi\u1ec3m  nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Welbeck ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c  Oblak trong pha \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t \u1edf ph\u00fat 21. M\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u00fat sau, Nacho Monreal b\u1eaft v\u00f4 l\u00ea nh\u01b0ng  v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tam the do cua Vrsaljko la buoc ngoat trong hiep mot tran Arsenal vs Atletico Madrid.\" title=\"T\u1ea5m th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf c\u1ee7a Vrsaljko l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Atletico Madrid.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/27/vrsaljko.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>T\u1ea5m th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf c\u1ee7a Vrsaljko l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Atletico Madrid.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00fat 33, Atletico c\u00f3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1p v\u1edbi c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Antoine Griezmann nh\u01b0ng  kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Ospina. Ph\u00fat 37, Partey \u0111i b\u00f3ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m  r\u1ed3i tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i cho Griezmann d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i \u0111i \u0111\u00fang v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7  th\u00e0nh Jan Oblak.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 n\u00f4n n\u00f3ng khi\u1ebfn Arsenal kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm  ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng khi \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid \u0111\u1ea7y tinh qu\u00e1i. Hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft th\u00fac  v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a 0-0.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong 15 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p hai, Arsenal ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c mi\u1ec7t m\u00e0i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n  th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Sau nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ed7 l\u01b0c, Alexandre Lacazette \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng  mang l\u1ea1i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Arsenal. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p b\u1eadt cao \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u ghi b\u00e0n t\u1eeb  qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Jack Wilshere.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Du bi don ep nhung Atletico Madrid van co ban thang go hoa nho cong cua Antoine Griezmann.\" title=\"D\u00f9 b\u1ecb d\u1ed3n \u00e9p nh\u01b0ng Atletico Madrid v\u1eabn c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Antoine Griezmann.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/27/griezmannn.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>D\u00f9 b\u1ecb d\u1ed3n \u00e9p nh\u01b0ng Atletico Madrid v\u1eabn c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Antoine Griezmann.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t b\u00e0n l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 v\u1edbi Arsenal khi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3  gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn. Ph\u00fat 69, Lacazette ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1eadt cao \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u  nh\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111i ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc. Trong 70 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn, t\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a  Arsenal l\u00e0 70%.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 khi kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u th\u1ebf. Ph\u00fat 81,  Antoine Griezmann v\u1edbi hai c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n cho Atletico, t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd  l\u1edbn. Th\u1eddi gan c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa  Arseanl vs Atletico Madrid k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-1.</p>\r\n<p><br>\r\n<strong>Nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ea1t (TTVN)</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1669","checkdouble":"185068"},{"date":"21:55 26/04","title":"Diego Simeone s\u1ee3 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a Arsenal?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/6/diego-simeone-so-nhat-cau-thu-nao-cua-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bott