x; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal v\u00e0 Atletico \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 Atletico Madrid v\u00e0 Arsenal \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. H\u1ecd l\u00e0 hai \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch song nh\u1eefng l\u00e1 th\u0103m may r\u1ee7i khi\u1ebfn hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Diego Simeone phat bieu ve tran Arsenal vs Atletico Madrid hinh anh\" title=\"Diego Simeone ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Atletico Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/26/Diego-Simeone-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Arsenal-vs-Atletico-Madrid-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Atletico \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u00e0 NHM \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft s\u1edbm c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. \u0110\u00eam nay Arsenal s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp Atletico tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, Arsenal ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1. Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 v\u1eeba c\u00f3 b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i West Ham v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Wenger chia tay Arsenal v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a, b\u1edfi v\u1eady c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League \u0111\u1ec3 chia tay \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111ang t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Emirates.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Atletico s\u1ee3 Mesut Ozil</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Diego Simeone ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/nhan-dinh-arsenal-vs-atletico-madrid-2h05-ngay-274-tat-ca-vi-wenger-184-185040.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal vs Atletico Madrid</span>, v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mesut Ozil b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ozil\" title=\"Ozil\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/6/vi-sao-mesut-ozil-vang-mat-o-tran-gap-west-ham.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Diego Simeone \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Mesut Ozil</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ozil c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u00e1ng kinh ng\u1ea1c, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Arsenal. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u1ebfn Ozil n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u00f4m h\u1eadn, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea3nh ch\u00e2n&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Atletico s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecbt k\u00edn nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec3 Ramsey hay Ozil tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ecdc khe. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u k\u1ef9 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Arsenal, t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eafc ch\u1ebf h\u1ecd&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSimeone c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao HLV Wenger: &ldquo;\u00d4ng \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng HLV v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u00f4ng \u1ea5y l\u00e0m cho Arsenal th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. \u0110\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u00f4ng \u1ea5y trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u1edf c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t th\u00fa v\u1ecb&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1668","checkd