gn: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Harry Redknapp noi ve Gareth Bale hinh anh\" title=\"Harry Redknapp n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Gareth Bale h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/19/Harry-Redknapp-noi-ve-Gareth-Bale-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gareth Bale mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/tiep-tuc-bi-zidane-bo-roi-gareth-bale-cay-cu-doi-den-bayern-180-185035.html\" target=\"_blank\"> Bale ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</span>, anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Bayern, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Los Blancos \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft C1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng Bale kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb Zidane lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng, anh \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n. Bale \u0111ang th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Bale, \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh MU v\u00e0 Tottenham mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Bayern Munich v\u00e0 PSG c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal \u0111\u00f2i 100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f3. Los Blancos c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Harry Redknapp khuy\u00ean Bale tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Tottenham</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Harry Redknapp n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Gareth Bale, c\u1ef1u HLV c\u1ee7a Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 khuy\u00ean ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales n\u00ean tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Spurs n\u1ebfu r\u1eddi Real Madrid.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gareth Bale cua Real\" title=\"Gareth Bale cua Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/tro-lai-tottenham-la-lua-chon-hoan-hao-voi-gareth-bale.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Redknapp khuy\u00ean Gareth Bale tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Tottenham</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201cBale \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Tottenham, n\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1eddi Real \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 v\u00e0 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Spurs s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 NHM Tottenham \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang mong ch\u1edd \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cBale \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 n\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1eddi Real c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u1ec9 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y Tottenham c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Bale. V\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Anh, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi Tottenham\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGareth Bale \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Real Madrid trong 5 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, anh c\u00f3 h\u01a1n 180 l\u1ea7n ra san v\u00e0 ghi 81 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u La Liga v\u00e0 3 Champions League, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ed1i l\u01b0\u01a1ng duy\u00ean gi\u1eefa Anh v\u00e0 Real s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1666","checkdouble":"185065"},{"date":"21:05 26/04","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh QBV 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/26/huyen-thoai-mu-du-doan-cai-ten-se-gianh-qbv-2018.PNG","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.