ilter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng 2018 s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 Lionel Messi thay nhau \u0111o\u1ea1t danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 hai ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, h\u1ecd duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gary Neville du doan Ronaldo se gianh Qua bong Vang 2018 hinh anh\" title=\"Gary Neville d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Ronaldo s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/26/huyen-thoai-mu-du-doan-cai-ten-se-gianh-qbv-2018.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u1ee8ng vi\u00ean cho danh hi\u1ec7u QBV 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y C\u1ea3 CR7 v\u00e0 M10 \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, h\u1ecd \u0111ang gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u. Messi gi\u00fap Barca v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00fap nh\u00e0 Vua T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch La Liga.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Ronaldo, anh \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t \u1edf Champions League gi\u00fap Real \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo v\u1eabn l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t cho danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, n\u0103m nay th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chen ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mohamed Salah c\u1ee7a Liverpool. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u00e3 ghi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, anh c\u00f3 43 b\u00e0n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i, Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u00e0o thua Salah. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 gi\u00fap Liverpool \u0111ang x\u1ebfp trong Top 3 \u1edf Premier League v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft C1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Gary Neville \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Ronaldo h\u01a1n Salah</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gary Neville n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng 2018, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Cristiano Ronaldo l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u1ed1 1 cho danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo lap ky luc moi\" title=\"Ronaldo lap ky luc moi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/26/ronaldo-lap-ky-luc-cup-c1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gary Neville tin Ronaldo s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201cSalah \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Ronaldo cao h\u01a1n. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 32 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u00fac n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i th\u00e1n ph\u1ee5c, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Ronaldo s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh QBV 2018\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cV\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Real \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League, n\u1ebfu Real c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0y Ronaldo g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a danh hi\u1ec7u QBV 2018, t\u00f4i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111o\u1ea1t gi\u1ea3i QBV k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2007\u00a0</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2007 - Kaka\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2008 - Ronaldo\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2009 - Messi\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2010 - Messi\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2011 - Messi\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2012 - Messi\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2013 - Ronaldo\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2014 - Ronaldo\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2015 - Messi\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2016 - Ronaldo\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2017 - Ronaldo\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2018 - ???</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1665","checkdouble":"185064"},{"date":"21:34 26/04","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1i \u01b0u c\u1ee7a Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc Swansea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/26/day-doi-hinh-toi-uu-cua-chelsea-truoc-swansea.png","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}