ackground:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng quan</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea3 Chelsea v\u00e0 Swansea \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t \u0111i\u1ec3m. The Blues \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 5 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng Premier League, k\u00e9m Top 4 kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i c\u00f2n 5 v\u00f2ng, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00e0o Top 4 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Conte l\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nhan dinh Swansea vs Chelsea vong 36 Ngoai hang Anh hinh anh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Swansea vs Chelsea v\u00f2ng 36 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/22/Nhan-dinh-Swansea-vs-Chelsea-vong-36-Ngoai-hang-Anh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Swansea \u1edf v\u00f2ng 36 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nSwansea \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 17 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n nh\u00f3m xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng c\u00f3 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. \u201cThi\u00ean nga \u0111en\u201d \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi nh\u00f3m nguy hi\u1ec3m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Swansea vs Chelsea v\u00f2ng 36 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m. Swansea c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 nh\u01b0ng Chelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>T\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">David Luiz v\u1eabn ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i. Danny Drinkwater \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, song kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Conte s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1eabn \u0111ang b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf.\u00a0<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Day! Doi hinh toi uu cua Chelsea truoc Swansea hinh anh 2\" title=\"\u0110\u00e2y! \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1i \u01b0u c\u1ee7a Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc Swansea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/29/Day!-Doi-hinh-toi-uu-cua-Chelsea-truoc-Swansea-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>David Luiz ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nEthan Ampadu ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n v\u00ec g\u00e3y m\u1eaft c\u00e1 ch\u00e2n, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 Pedro hay Hazard \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u00c1n treo gi\u00f2</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Marcos Alonso b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o v\u1edbi Shane Long, anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Swansea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>1 \u2013 </strong>Swansea ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1 trong 13 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea, 12 tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i h\u1ecd h\u00f2a 4 v\u00e0 thua 8.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>2 \u2013</strong> Sau 3 tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf Premier League. L\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng h\u1ecd th\u1eafng 3 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf Premier League l\u00e0 v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 9 n\u0103m 2017.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>50 -</strong> Antonio Conte \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 49 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng sau 72 tr\u1eadn \u1edf Premier League, n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Swansea anh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 50 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1i \u01b0u c\u1ee7a Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc Swansea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh toi uu cua Chelsea truoc Swansea\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1i \u01b0u c\u1ee7a Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc Swansea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/26/day-doi-hinh-toi-uu-cua-chelsea-truoc-swansea.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1i \u01b0u c\u1ee7a Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc Swansea</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1664","checkdouble":"185066"},{"date":"22:41 26/04","title":"Liverpool ph\u1ea3i mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/26/liverpool-phai-mua-cau-thu-nay-neu-muon-co-danh-hieu-lon.PNG","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.ad