 \u0111\u1ee7 v\u1edbi Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Klopp l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh \u1edf Champions League v\u00e0 Premier League. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, C\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Liverpool, Ray Clemence kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Liverpool n\u00ean mua m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Simon Mignolet v\u00e0 Loris Karius kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Liverpool h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cKlopp c\u1ea7n \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 s\u1ed1 1 m\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m\u201d.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ray Clemence khuy\u00ean Liverpool mua Butland</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Liverpool, Ray Clemence \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khuy\u00ean <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/day-muc-tieu-so-1-cua-liverpool-o-he-2018-172-181789.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Jack Butland</span> c\u1ee7a Stoke. Th\u00f4ng tin Liverpool quan t\u00e2m Butland \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1eeb l\u00e2u, Clemence mu\u1ed1n The Kop th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Butland\" title=\"Butland\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/26/liverpool-phai-mua-cau-thu-nay-neu-muon-co-danh-hieu-lon.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Clemence khuy\u00ean Liverpool mua Butland</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft Jack Butland t\u1eeb khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y 15 tu\u1ed5i, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 16 tu\u1ed5i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t, Butland s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nghe nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c Liverpool quan t\u00e2m c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n Klopp nhanh ch\u00f3ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Butland c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7u ti\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u1edf Liverpool\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRay Clemence c\u0169ng tin Liverpool s\u1ebd v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y: \u201c\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 5-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Roma gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1, Liverpool s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Roma \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1663","checkdouble":"185070"},{"date":"23:56 26/04","title":"\u201cArsenal kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn v\u00ec Mourinho\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2015/8/3/Diem-tin-Bongda24h-sang-ngay-89-Conte-hua-khong-bat-hoc-tro-da-trai-keo-hinh-anh-4.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px