argin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Mourinho khi\u1ebfn Arsenal g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong h\u01a1n 10 n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y Arsenal kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh hi\u1ec7u FA Cup l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 nh\u1ea5t. C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u00e0 Champions League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Martin Keown phat bieu ve Arsenal khien HLV Wenger dau long hinh anh\" title=\"Martin Keown ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal khi\u1ebfn HLV Wenger \u0111au l\u00f2ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2015/8/3/Diem-tin-Bongda24h-sang-ngay-89-Conte-hua-khong-bat-hoc-tro-da-trai-keo-hinh-anh-4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Martin Keown cho r\u1eb1ng Arsenal kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn v\u00ec Mourinho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nMartin Keown ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal, c\u1ef1u sao Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn trong h\u01a1n 10 n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;N\u0103m 2004 sau khi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Porto, Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Roman Abramovich \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Chelsea. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf Premier League \u0111\u00e3 thay&nbsp;\u0111\u1ed5i. Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n v\u00e0 mang v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c chi qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n \u1edf TTCN, Chelsea tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf l\u1ef1c \u1edf Anh. M.U v\u00e0 Arsenal c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n. Sau \u0111\u00f3 Man City c\u0169ng \u0111i theo con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a Arsenal c\u00e0ng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a Martin Keown kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd b\u1edfi Chelsea v\u00e0 Man City c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh nh\u1edd \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5t l\u00f9i b\u1edfi kh\u00f4ng chi qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Martin Keown n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Wenger</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Martin Keown kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh HLV Wenger chia tay Arsenal \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd: &ldquo;C\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u00f4ng \u1ea5y n\u00ean d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y n\u00ean nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u00e1t khao l\u1edbn h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1ea5y&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cac cau thu nhan dinh Arsenal vs Atletico Madrid se la mon qua tang rieng cho Wenger.\" title=\"C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Arsenal vs Atletico Madrid s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u00f3n qu\u00e0 t\u1eb7ng ri\u00eang cho Wenger.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/26/Arsenal-vs-Atletico-Madrid-(2h05-ngay-274)-Tat-ca-vi-Wenger-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Keown ch\u00fac Wenger v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League c\u00f9ng Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Wenger s\u1ebd chia tay Arsenal v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u, hy v\u1ecdng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Arsenal \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00eam nay, Arsenal ti\u1ebfp Atletico \u1edf s\u00e2n Emirates trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Europa League, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf<br>\r\ntr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1662","checkdouble":"185072"},{"date":"18:03 26/04","title":"HLV U16 Iran: K\u1ef3 t\u00edch c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/9/22/hlv-u16-iran-ky-tich-cua-u23-viet-nam-khong-noi-nen-dieu-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}.articlerelate2{padding:6px;min-height:72px}div.articlerelate2>a{color:#000;tex