111\u1ea5u VCK U16 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 20/9 \u0111\u1ebfn 7/10 t\u1ea1i Malaysia.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng C c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i Iran, \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9 v\u00e0 Indonesia. Trong c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0y, Iran \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t. N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV Hossein Moradi c\u1ee7a \u0110T U16 Iran t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV U16 Iran Ky tich cua U23 Viet Nam khong noi nen dieu gi hinh anh\" title=\"HLV U16 Iran K\u1ef3 t\u00edch c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/26/HLV-U16-Iran-Ky-tich-cua-U23-Viet-Nam-khong-noi-nen-dieu-gi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV U16 Iran tin r\u1eb1ng U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft:&nbsp; &quot;\u0110\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ec5, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u1eabn \u0111ang chia \u0111\u1ec1u cho 4 \u0111\u1ed9i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9 5 l\u1ea7n trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi T\u00e2y \u00c1. V\u00ec v\u1eady trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1, b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu...&quot;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 k\u1ef3 t\u00edch gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00c1 qu\u00e2n ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i U23 v\u1eeba qua, HLV U16 Iran cho r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 U16 v\u00e0 U23 kh\u00e1c nhau n\u00ean v\u1ecb n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng t\u1ecf ra qu\u00e1 lo ng\u1ea1i. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Moradi chia s\u1ebb: &quot;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1c, \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i U16 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 \u0111ang ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, b\u1ea3ng C v\u1eabn l\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng&quot;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 t\u1ecf ra th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi tuy nhi\u00ean HLV Hossein Moradi v\u1eabn nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau tr\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a U16 Iran l\u00e0 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 U17 World Cup 2019.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1ea3i U16 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb 20/9 \u0111\u1ebfn 7/10 t\u1ea1i Malaysia. B\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n cho ch\u00e2u \u00c1 d\u1ef1 World Cup U17 t\u1ea1i Peru n\u0103m 2019.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Viet Nam o bang dau vua phai tai le boc tham VCK U16 chau A 2018\" title=\"Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea1i l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m VCK U16 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/26/DbsUTCsWkAAiiD6.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea1i l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m VCK U16 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thanh Long (TTVN)</span></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1661","checkdouble":"185060"},{"date":"18:33 26/04","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 26/04: MU mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2013/1/216875hp2-20131194452.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2