ld; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Diem tin toi 2604 MU muon dua nguoi cu tro lai Old Trafford hinh anh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 2604 MU mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/17/Diem-tin-toi-2604-MU-muon-dua-nguoi-cu-tro-lai-Old-Trafford-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU mu\u1ed1n mua l\u1ea1i Jonny Evans</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTheo The Sun, MU mu\u1ed1n mua l\u1ea1i trung v\u1ec7 Jonny Evans t\u1eeb West Brom. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p West Brom xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 3 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Gerrard c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV c\u1ee7a Rangers</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Liverpool, Steven Gerrard \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CLB Rangers nh\u1eafm ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal chi 40 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Rugani</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Calciomercato, Arsenal \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi 40 tri\u1ec7u euro mua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Daniele Rugani c\u1ee7a Juventus. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin do \u00e1p l\u1ef1c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Iniesta \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e1c r\u1eddi Barca</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Andres Iniesta s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 r\u1eddi Barca v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, th\u1ee9 6 tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Alderweireld kh\u00f4ng t\u1edbi MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"trung ve Toby Alderweireld\" title=\"trung ve Toby Alderweireld\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/Se-la-sai-lam-neu-Tottenham-ban-Alderweireld-cho-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sol Campbell kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Toby Alderweireld kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sol Campbell kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Toby Alderweireld c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Tottenham \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn M.U, Spurs s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u1edf Premier League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb d\u00e0nh cho Salah</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Daily Mail kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb d\u00e0nh cho ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mohamed Salah, The Kop quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>MU \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Man City v\u00ec sao Napoli</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Mirror, MU ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho c\u1ee7a Napoli v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 6 n\u00e0y, hi\u1ec7n Man City c\u0169ng \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Boateng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Bayern</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Bayern v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Jerome Boateng c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 Premier League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Man City kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao cho Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bruyne Man City\" title=\"Bruyne Man City\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/23/nhung-diem-nhan-rut-ra-sau-tran-man-city-50-swansea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Man City kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n De Bruyne v\u00e0 Sterling cho Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd Manchester Evening News, Man City s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho Real Madrid. Hi\u1ec7n Los Blancos \u0111ang quan t\u00e2m Leroy Sane, Kevin De Bruyne, Raheem Sterling v\u00e0 John Stones c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng chi ti\u00eau nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Evening Standard, Chelsea s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng chi ti\u00eau nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n l\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 chi qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n \u1edf hai k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1660","checkdouble":"185063"},{"date":"18:33 26/04","title":"Ramsey: \"Arteta s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV gi\u1ecfi trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/7/ramsey-arteta-se-tro-thanh-hlv-gioi-trong-tuong-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContaine