#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Salah \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mohamed Salah \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u1edbi 31 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Roy Keane phat bieu ve Mohamed Salah hinh anh\" title=\"Roy Keane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mohamed Salah h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/25/Roy-Keane-phat-bieu-ve-Mohamed-Salah-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Salah \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nN\u1ebfu t\u00ednh tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn, Salah \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 43 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Anh c\u0169ng \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y V\u00e0ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Salah \u0111ang gi\u00fap Liverpool l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o Top 3 Premier League v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft C1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHuy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Liverpool, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/goc-liverpool-salah-da-thuc-su-la-cau-thu-dang-cap-the-gioi-172-183960.html\" target=\"_blank\">Steven Gerrard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Salah</span>, anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u sao Roma t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n&nbsp;t\u1ea1i. Gerrard c\u0169ng tin r\u1eb1ng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Salah c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Salah v\u00e0 Ronaldo.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Roy Keane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Salah</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Roy Keane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mohamed Salah, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a M.U kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Liverpool ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngang h\u00e0ng v\u1edbi Lionel Messi v\u00e0 Cristiano Ronaldo n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Salah toa sang voi 2 ban, 2 duong kien tao. Anh deu khong an mung nhu su ton trong CLB cu\" title=\"Salah t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi 2 b\u00e0n, 2 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. Anh \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0103n m\u1eebng nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng CLB c\u0169\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/25/liverpool-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-real-vu-salah.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Roy Keane n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Salah&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n&ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Salah kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 thua k\u00e9m Ronaldo hay Messi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngang h\u00e0ng v\u1edbi hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Salah c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0y m\u1edbi gi\u00fap c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 so s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi Ronaldo hay Messi. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Roma v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-2 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League, Roy Keane tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Roma s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Roma s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i d\u1ed3n l\u00ean ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1, nh\u01b0ng Liverpool ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfp. T\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng Liverpool s\u1ebd \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Roma l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Barca&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1658","checkdouble":"185062"},{"date":"12:07 26/04","title":"B\u1ea7u T\u00fa r\u00fat lui, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i lo v\u1ec1 qu\u00ea l\u00e0m ru\u1ed9ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/14/bau-tu-rut-lui-vien-canh-cong-phuong-ve-que-lam-ruong-khep-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px