border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eefa b\u1ea7u T\u00fa v\u00e0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i VFF kh\u00f3a VIII, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 Ban ch\u1ea5p h\u00e0nh kh\u00f3a t\u1edbi khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed3ng quan \u0111i\u1ec3m. Vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea7u T\u00fa m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, nh\u01b0 Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch H\u0110QT ki\u00eam T\u1ed5ng Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c VPF, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Tr\u01b0\u1edfng Ban \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh V-League 2018 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed gh\u1ebf Ph\u00f3 Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch ph\u1ee5 tr\u00e1ch T\u00e0i ch\u00ednh VFF khi\u1ebfn b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HAGL cong phuong\" title=\"HAGL c\u00f4ng ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/bau-tu-rut-lui-vien-canh-cong-phuong-ve-que-lam-ruong-khep-lai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>B\u1ea7u T\u00fa nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ed9, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i lo v\u1ec1 qu\u00ea l\u00e0m ru\u1ed9ng.&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi ng\u1ed3i nhi\u1ec1u chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf s\u1ebd l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m t\u00ednh ph\u1ea3n bi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-viet-nam-c168-p1.html\" title=\"b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 vi\u1ec7t nam\" type=\"b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 vi\u1ec7t nam\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></span>, y\u00eau c\u1ea7u b\u1ea7u T\u00fa r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ee7 ch\u1ed1t. B\u1ea7u Th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ed3ng quan \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c khi cho bi\u1ebft s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 cho Long An n\u1eefa n\u1ebfu b\u1ea7u T\u00fa kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ed9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m &quot;l\u00e0m cho ra nh\u1ebd&quot;. Ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u nh\u01b0 vi\u1ec7c d\u1ecda gi\u1ea3i th\u1ec3 HAGL, \u0111\u1ec3 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1ec1 qu\u00ea l\u00e0m ru\u1ed9ng, hay r\u00fat HAGL kh\u1ecfi V-League \u0111\u1ec3 sang m\u1ed9t n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 kh\u00e1c th\u00e0nh l\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Khi b\u1ea7u T\u00fa nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ed9</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, b\u1ea7u T\u00fa x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng tham gia \u1ee9ng c\u1eed v\u1ecb tr\u00ed Ph\u00f3 Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch ph\u1ee5 tr\u00e1ch t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a VFF kh\u00f3a t\u1edbi. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i &quot;h\u1ea1 nhi\u1ec7t&quot; tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i VFF kh\u00f3a VIII khi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh th\u1eddi gian qua &quot;c\u0103ng nh\u01b0 d\u00e2y \u0111\u00e0n&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin, b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 vui m\u1eebng khi chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean Zing: &quot;Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a anh T\u00fa r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Anh T\u00fa t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian ch\u0103m s\u00f3c cho VPF. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t hoan ngh\u00eanh v\u00e0 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng d\u0169ng c\u1ea3m \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a anh T\u00fa. HAGL ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i V.League v\u00e0 c\u00f2n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n, gi\u00fap b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea7u T\u00fa r\u00fat lui, hai \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed PVT ph\u1ee5 tr\u00e1ch t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh VFF kh\u00f3a t\u1edbi g\u1ed3m \u00f4ng Tr\u1ea7n V\u0103n Li\u00eang - Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch H\u0110QT c\u00f4ng ty c\u1ed5 ph\u1ea7n Ca cao Vi\u1ec7t Nam, c\u00f9ng \u00f4ng L\u00ea V\u0103n Th\u00e0nh - Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch H\u0110QT c\u00f4ng ty c\u1ed5 ph\u1ea7n \u0110\u1ed9ng L\u1ef1c ki\u00eam ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n B\u00f3ng chuy\u1ec1n Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng:</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/vleague/ghi-ban-dau-tien-tai-vleague-2018-cong-phuong-noi-gi-291-184743.html\">Ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i V-League 2018, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/vleague/cong-phuong-ghi-ban-hlv-duong-minh-ninh-khen-co-dong-vien-hagl-291-184738.html\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ghi b\u00e0n, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh khen m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-hagl-vs-da-nang-17h00-ngay-214-vleague-2018-372-184714.html\">HAGL 2-0 \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng (KT): C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ebft t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bo-doi-tru-cot-u23-mo-ve-du-world-cup-cung-dt-viet-nam-168-184578.html\">B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t U23 m\u01a1 v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 World Cup c\u00f9ng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hagl-di-xuong-cong-phuong-thay-nho-tuan-anh-o-tuyen-giua-168-184387.html\">HAGL \u0111i xu\u1ed1ng, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ea5y nh\u1edb Tu\u1ea5n Anh \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/vleague/hlv-hagl-cung-phai-phat-buc-vi-cong-phuong-291-184340.html\">HLV HAGL c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ph\u00e1t b\u1ef1c v\u00ec C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)&nbsp;</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1657","checkdouble":"185047"},{"date":"14:55 26/04","title":"HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi b\u1ea7u T\u00fa kh\u00f4ng tranh c\u1eed VFF?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/14/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-noi-gi-sau-khi-bau-tu-khong-tranh-cu-vff.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px